name: Excel Electrical
overview:
Since our establishment is in year 1974, we, “Excel Electrical” are a trustworthy organization engaged in manufacturing and supplying a comprehensive range of Knobs, handles & Allied Products and Rust Prevention Chemicals. Under this affordable range, we offer Big Square Knob, Button Knob, Seven Star Knob, Clutch Crompton Set, Clutch Set and MS Stand.

Our Team: Procuring agents Quality controllers Warehousing and packaging unit R&D personnel

Our Infrastructure: With the support of our strong infrastructure facility, we are able to develop a quality assured range of Knobs, handles & Allied Products and Rust Prevention Chemicals. Outfitted with modern amenities like technically advanced technology, sophisticated machinery and ultra-modern equipment, our infrastructure is spread across an extensive area of land.

Our Quality: Quality being a main concern for our organization, we lay special emphasis on the quality of our offered range of Knobs, handles & Allied Products and Rust Prevention Chemicals. To offer qualitative range of knobs, we utilize quality-approved raw material and other basic components, which are obtained from reliable vendors of the industry.

Why Us?: Our entire range of Equipment and Machinery Consumables are widely demanded in the market for its high quality and on-time delivery. Owing to our transparent business practices and streamlined business operations, we have been able to garner a huge client base across the nation.

Client Satisfaction: Gaining satisfaction of our clients immensely is the utmost goal of our organization. To attain the same, we manufacture our entire range of Knobs, handles & Allied Products and Rust Prevention Chemicals with utmost perfection.
